# OPTIONAL. The app is bring-your-own-key: players paste their own Groq key into
# the UI (the key button), stored in their browser. You only need this file if
# you want a fallback server key for local dev so you don't paste one each time.
#
# Get a free key at https://console.groq.com/keys
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill it in.
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...
